OL,3,CMum of 12-year-old rioter on Ibiza
OL,4,Choliday while he attended court
OL,6,FThe mother of a 12-year-old boy
OL,7,Finvolved in rioting has been ordered
OL,8,Fby a judge to appear in court - after
OL,9,Fshe chose to fly to Ibiza instead of
OL,10,Fattending the hearing.
OL,12,FDistrict Judge Joanne Hirst said she
OL,13,Fwas "frankly astonished" the boy's
OL,14,Fmother was abroad on a five-day
OL,15,Fsunshine break, after he admitted two
OL,16,Fcounts of violent disorder.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
