OL,3,CMum of 12-year-old rioter on Ibiza
OL,4,Choliday while he attended court
OL,6,FShe adjourned sentencing of the boy -
OL,7,Fwho is too young to be named - and
OL,8,Fordered a parental summons so the
OL,9,Fmother must appear before the court to
OL,10,Fexplain her actions.
OL,12,FThe boy was accompanied to Manchester
OL,13,FMagistrates' Court by his uncle and
OL,14,Fhad earlier admitted being part of a
OL,15,Fmob that attacked a bus outside a
OL,16,Fhotel housing asylum seekers in
OL,17,FManchester on 31 July.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
