OL,3,CMum of 12-year-old rioter on Ibiza
OL,4,Choliday while he attended court
OL,6,FDays later on 3 August, in Manchester
OL,7,Fcity centre, he was part of a group
OL,8,Ffilmed kicking the windows of a vape
OL,9,Fshop and throwing a missile at a
OL,10,Fpolice van.
OL,12,FDozens of towns and cities saw
OL,13,Fviolence erupt following the killing
OL,14,Fof three young girls at a Taylor Swift
OL,15,Fthemed dance class in Southport on 29
OL,16,FJuly.
OL,18,FDistrict Judge Hirst was told the
OL,19,Fboy's mother was not present, having
OL,20,Fbooked a holiday in July and gone
OL,21,Fabroad.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
