OL,3,CMum of 12-year-old rioter on Ibiza
OL,4,Choliday while he attended court
OL,6,FShe thanked the boy's uncle for
OL,7,Faccompanying his nephew to court in
OL,8,Fhis mother's absence, but added: "One
OL,9,Fday before the hearing we find out the
OL,10,Fmum has gone on holiday and is not
OL,11,Fwith her son who played a greater part
OL,12,Fin the recent civil disorder than any
OL,13,Fadult or child I've seen coming
OL,14,Fthrough these courts. I'm frankly
OL,15,Fastonished.
OL,17,F"I will require a full explanation
OL,18,Ffrom mum on her decision to go on
OL,19,Fholiday one day before her 12-year-old
OL,20,Fson comes to court facing a potential
OL,21,Fcustodial sentence.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
