OL,3,CMum of 12-year-old rioter on Ibiza
OL,4,Choliday while he attended court
OL,6,F"This is a serious situation, it has
OL,7,Fnow deteriorated in my view because of
OL,8,Fthe actions of the mother.
OL,10,F"She is on notice - I will be
OL,11,Fchallenging her about this decision."
OL,13,FAddressing the boy as she adjourned
OL,14,Fsentencing to 11 September, Judge
OL,15,FHirst told him: "Boys like you need
OL,16,Ftheir mums in their lives. I need your
OL,17,Fmum here."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
