OL,3,CMum of 12-year-old rioter on Ibiza
OL,4,Choliday while he attended court
OL,6,FIn a separate hearing in the same
OL,7,Fcourt, a 16-year-old boy was told he
OL,8,Fwas being given "the biggest chance in
OL,9,Fyour life" by Judge Hirst, who decided
OL,10,Fto pass a referral order rather than
OL,11,Fjail the youngster.
OL,13,FThe teenager, accompanied by his
OL,14,Fmother, had admitted violent disorder
OL,15,Fby throwing a bottle at a police horse
OL,16,Fduring wide scale trouble in Bolton
OL,17,Ftown centre in July.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
