OL,3,CMum of 12-year-old rioter on Ibiza
OL,4,Choliday while he attended court
OL,6,FThe court heard the youngster's father
OL,7,Fhad died and his mother, who
OL,8,Faccompanied him to court, was having
OL,9,Ftreatment for cancer.
OL,11,FHe was asked by the judge: "What were
OL,12,Fyou thinking?"
OL,14,FThe boy replied: "I was not really
OL,15,Fthinking anything. We came into town
OL,16,Fand everything just erupted.
OL,17,FAdrenaline. I'm disgusted with myself."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
