OL,3,CMum of 12-year-old rioter on Ibiza
OL,4,Choliday while he attended court
OL,6,FThe youngster's mother told the court:
OL,7,F"He's frightened to death of going to
OL,8,Fprison. I think this has been a
OL,9,Fmassive wake-up call."
OL,11,FThe judge warned the youngster he had
OL,12,Fnarrowly avoided custody and instead
OL,13,Fgave him a 12-month referral order
OL,14,Fwith intensive supervision and a
OL,15,Fcurfew.
OL,17,FShe added: "It was mindless violence.
OL,18,FI'm going to give you a chance. This
OL,19,Fis the biggest chance in your life
OL,20,Fthat you will get."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
